{
  "stem": "23090.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were-- we thought it was the Allies, or we thought someone was coming to liberate us, when, in fact, we discovered that the Germans were focusing all their artillery and trying to kill us and destroy us while we were still in the camp.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were liberated and then we were told by our liberators, the Americans, that-- we were asking them, why were you shelling.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why were you-- they say, it wasn't us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was, in fact, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they captured, they captured part of that artillery unit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I just laid under-- again, under that window there and just waited, and waited, and waited until it was silence.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And for hours, we sat quietly, not hearing anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in the morning, it was, again, in the morning--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We waited-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there was silence.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After this barrage for three or four days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All of a sudden it got very quiet, and so we didn't want to move.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know what was going on, so we must have laid there for hours, or maybe a full day, until we finally were hearing some voices, some strange voices.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not German voice, not German language, it wasn't-- it was like-- it wasn't Russian either.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we started peaking our heads above these windows and we started seeing these guys with yellow-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Scarves.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they looked like the American cowboys, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they're pulling up with tanks and everything else.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, all hell broke loose and they tried to contain us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, they were wonderful to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
